{"tid":1632352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術必睇！]防止陣容潰散同集體恐慌嘅方法","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T17:22:10.000Z","uid":53698,"like":138,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"b2eb17567b38ab25f99262b828df8d3fe505d11f","tid":1632352,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:41:48.000Z","msg":"上次開過post 但太長氣 所以冇咩人睇 <br />\n所以開多次 希望大家花啲時間睇睇<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n1. <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中後排請分開左右兩邊企。</span></strong></span><br />\na.預留中線予前線人員撤退，同時<br />\nb.俾人傳遞物資、roadblock 嘅空間。<br />\nc.俾後排嘅人睇到前線發生咩事，避免資訊不完全而引發集體恐慌情緒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 每平方米最多只能企4個人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人同人之間約保持一米左右距離，切勿人貼人。</strong></span></span><br />\n<em>現場太擁擠會加劇群眾恐慌傳染和誇大化</em><br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">事前決定好逃生路線</span></strong></span><br />\n當有突發狀況出現時盡可能帶領人群有序循住既定路線/出口撤退。<br />\n<br />\n3.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同熟人組隊</strong></span></span><br />\n如果在事件當下有朋友、親人等熟悉的人在身旁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>當群眾出現大恐慌時，自我保護的方法。</strong></span></span><br />\n<em>以下部份嘅嘢我都只係copy and paste。</em><br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在移動時像拳擊手一樣把雙手護在胸前</span></strong></span><br />\na.確保移動空間<br />\nb.確保呼吸空間。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>跌倒了要防禦好</strong></span></span><br />\n以雙手護著頭部、胸部，並將雙腿蜷曲起來行胎兒姿勢防禦。<br />\n<br />\n頭盔:我唔係讀心理學出身，純粹真心想解決陣容太過容易因為恐慌而潰散嘅問題，所以上網搵咗有關群眾心理嘅理論，睇吓有冇解決辦法，希望有更多專業人士幫手提出建議，一齊討論吓點樣先可以避免啲人過度恐慌而出現人踩人嘅情況出現。"},{"pid":"5b6109c8ef9bb4cbe74329fc6facbf38ca104acb","tid":1632352,"uid":15259,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"7fa54e5f961579b081d7a09a46c836f0958ceda5","tid":1632352,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"話你知咩叫和勇合一<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630017</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ffbacd12e40ec33fe1d33b4bdfcb99928b05e4d","tid":1632352,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"唉，睇一條片，教你點收啲黑紅藍皮，唔好話唔教精你地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632259</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3adc90a21c0fd1c5794f31ea2ebea75e060523a2","tid":1632352,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"推 希望大家睇一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6081bd4c7bffff68af7fc155b2d2c409ab4198","tid":1632352,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773175c8a9cc77b68e5b74e74c388560159b635a","tid":1632352,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a338eed1818472dca102845f977ecdd597b8067","tid":1632352,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836553e17335514d41e2ae439db5956634b8d75d","tid":1632352,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2909ba04b5bc